name: sentieon-genomics
description:
Sentieon provides complete solutions for secondary DNA analysis. Our
software improves upon BWA, GATK, Mutect, and Mutect2 based pipelines.
The Sentieon tools are deployable on any CPU-based computing system. Use
of this software is subject to the EULA at:
https://www.sentieon.com/EULA/eula-aws.html Please set the path to the
sentieon license server with: export SENTIEON_LICENSE=[FQDN]:[PORT]
